data.description: Just 35 minutes from Ft. Leonard Wood, on well kept roads, & accessed through a security gate; This move in ready, 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom, fully furnished home on 36 acres of mature hardwood timber offers the opportunity to embrace nature while being conveniently near the amenities of the military base & its supporting infrastructure. Nestled within the heart of the Ozarks, this home combines modern comfort, connectivity, & security features while still maintaining its homesteading potential, providing an escape for those seeking a connection with the land & ready to move now. Step onto the private back deck & breathe in the crisp air as you soak in the beauty of your private haven. The workshop with power is able to accommodate endless possibilities. Many local treasures such as: Lake of the Ozarks State Park, Clifty Creek Natural Bridge, & others are just a short drive away. Claim this tranquil retreat that is ready for you to move right in before it becomes a missed opportunity.
